{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"OUDSSwitchItem","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some swith components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a switch with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Layouts","text":"Layouts","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","text":"Indicator states","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","text":"Particular cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as disabled."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                   helper: \"1967\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/18acc0-switch","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading"},{"level